<H1>SpaceZone salutes the employees of NASA</H1><BR>
<P>




Over the past three and a half decades the former and current ranks of NASA employees have been deeply committed to space research and to the dissemination of information concerning its activities and findings. The tireless efforts and endless hours of dedication from thousands of men and women working as a team, have made NASA the premier space agency in the world.
<P>
NASA&#39;s open policy regarding its information has unlocked the doors of space exploration, new knowledge and discovery to countless numbers of individuals and organizations across globe. Educators, students and space enthusiasts alike have come to rely on NASA as the primary source of space-related information. 
<P>
In this spirit, SpaceZone commends all NASA personnel on a job well done.

<P>




