<H1>Shuttle Mission STS-80</H1><BR>

<H2>Mission Timeline</H2>
<BR CLEAR="all">
<P>&nbsp;

<p align=center><i>Note: All times are Central Standard Time (GMT -0600)</i></p>
<p><A HREF="d1.html">Flight Day 1</A> - Launch, ORFEUS-SPAS deploy
<p><A HREF="d2.html">Flight Day 2</A> - Experiment operations: CMIX, OSVS, CAPL 
