<p><A HREF="d9.html">Flight Day 9</A> - EVA preparations in middeck 
<p><A HREF="d10.html">Flight Day 10</A> - First EVA, testing International Space Station tools
<p><A HREF="d11.html">Flight Day 11</A> - Preparation for second EVA, SPAS rendezvous burn
<p><A HREF="d12.html">Flight Day 12</A> - Second EVA, using robot arm
