<HTML>
<HEAD>
	<TITLE>SPACEZONE &#149; SPACE NEWS</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<!--Copyrigh© 1996 Warner International Communications Group, Inc. All Rights Reserved.-->
<P><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#1113AB" VLINK="#B40FB"
ALINK="#F0051" >
<BODY>

<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="395" HEIGHT="119" SRC="art/szlogo.gif" ALT="SpaceZone">
<BR CLEAR="all">
<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="198" HEIGHT="198" SRC="art/patch.gif"ALT="STS-79 Patch">
<BR>
<P>
<H1>Astronaut Exchange
<BR>Shuttle Mission STS-79</H1>
<BR><H2>Mission Time Line</H2>
<P>
<BR CLEAR="all">



 <p align=center><i>Note: All times are Central Daylight Time (GMT
-0500)</i></p>
<center>
<table border=0 width=600 cellspacing=10 border=0>
<tr>
<td><br></td><td width=400 align=left valign=top><font size="+1">
<A HREF="15.htm">Flight Day 1</A> - Launch, Spacehab activation</font>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><br></td><td width=400 align=left valign=top><font size="+1">
<A HREF="16.htm">Flight Day 2</A> - Rendezvous burn, Spacehab setup,
SAREX equipment test</font> 
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><br></td><td width=400 align=left valign=top><font size="+1">
<A HREF="17.htm">Flight Day 3</A> - Rendezvous burn, video tour of
Spacehab, SAREX operations</font>
</td></tr>
<tr>
