<!--Volume 8-->
<P>
<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="172" HEIGHT="131" SRC="art/v8.jpg">

<A NAME="v8"><FONT SIZE="+1"><B>Houston, We&#39;ve Got a Problem</B></FONT></A>
<BR>
35 minutes<BR>
Introduced by Astronaut <A HREF="walt.htm">Walt Cunningham</A>
<P>
"Houston, we've got a problem... There was a definite loud bang." These shocking words came down from Apollo 13 with the force of a meteor. America had just previously landed its second successful mission on the moon. In the confidence and glory, something was overlooked.
<P>
Watch this exciting video with never-before-seen footage of this almost tragic mission. And watch and see how  human spirit, how American ingenuity, saved the day.
<P>
<P>
