<!--Volume 26-->
<P>
<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="172" HEIGHT="131" SRC="art/blank.jpg">

<A NAME="v26"><FONT SIZE="+1"><B>We Deliver</B></FONT></A>
<BR>
35 minutes<BR>
Introduced by Astronaut Bob Overmyer
<P>
This video is a showcase of space firsts. You&#39;ll see the first American woman in space, the first Afro-American astronaut, and the first spacewalk in nine years using a new spacesuit design and portable life support pack. 
<P>
This video captures the shuttle in orbit, as well as the deployment of two communication satellites. This series of missions linked a communications network giving constant contact between ground control and the astronauts. Watch this exciting display of America&#39;s space program at its finest.
<P>
<IMG BORDER="0" ALIGN="middle" WIDTH="39" HEIGHT="34" SRC="art/film.gif">We Deliver QuickTime sample available soon.
<P>
<IMG BORDER="0" ALIGN="middle" WIDTH="46" HEIGHT="25" SRC="art/ra.gif">
Audio sample available soon.
