ALINK="#F0051" >
<BODY>

<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="395" HEIGHT="119" SRC="art/szlogo.gif" ALT="SpaceZone">
<BR CLEAR="all">
<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="189" HEIGHT="190" SRC="art/80patch.gif"ALT="STS-80 Patch">
<BR>
<P>

<H1>Shuttle Mission STS-80</H1><BR>

<P>
<A HREF="80time.htm">Back to Mission Timeline</A>
<BR CLEAR="all">
<b>November 24, 1996</b><dl>
<dt>12:53 pm
<dd>
Crew wakeup


<dt>03:53 pm
<dd>
Jernigan, Jones and Musgrave begin 5 hours of off-duty time


<dt>04:28 pm
<dd>
Cockrell and Rominger conduct another rendezvous burn to maintain distance with the WSF and ORFEUS-SPAS satellites before beginning their off-duty period


<dt>09:53 pm
<dd>
Jernigan resumes work with the VIEW-CAPL experiment


<dt>10:23 pm
<dd>
PAO Opportunity with Rominger, Jones and Musgrave


<dt>10:53 pm
<dd>
Rominger exercises


<dt>11:23 pm
<dd>
Cockrell exercises


<dt>12:03 am
<dd>
Rominger picks up work with the VIEW-CAPL experiment


<dt>12:23 am
<dd>
Crew Choice TV with Jernigan


<dt>12:53 am
<dd>
Musgrave exercises</dl>

<p><b>November 25, 1996</b><dl>
<dt>01:23 am
<dd>
Jones exercises


<dt>01:43 am
<dd>
Cockrell checks on the rodents which are part of the PARE-NIH experiment


<dt>01:53 am
<dd>
Jernigan exercises


<dt>02:32 am
<dd>
Cockrell and Rominger conduct another rendezvous burn to maintain distance with the WSF and ORFEUS-SPAS satellites


<dt>04:23 am
<dd>
Private medical conference


<dt>04:38 am
<dd>
Private family conference for Cockrell, Rominger and Jernigan


<dt>05:53 am
<dd>
Crew sleep begins</dl>






