<p><b>December 5, 1996</b><dl>
<dt>01:35 am
<dd>
Deorbit prep begins


<dt>02:57 am
<dd>
PLBD closing


<dt>05:37 am
<dd>
Deorbit burn


<dt>06:37 am
<dd>
COLUMBIA LANDS AT THE KENNEDY SPACE CENTER</dl>






