<H1>Astronaut Exchange
<BR>Shuttle Mission STS-79</H1>
<BR>

 <H2><A HREF="time.htm">Mission Timeline</A></H2>
 <H2>Flight Day 1</H2>
 
 <BR CLEAR="all">
 
 <b>September 16, 1996</b>
<dl>
<dt>03:54 a.m.
<dd>Launch

<p>
<dt>04:37 a.m.
<dd>OMS-2

<p>
<dt>05:19 a.m.
<dd>PLBD opening

<p>
<dt>06:24 a.m.
<dd>Apt and Walz begin to activate Spacehab systems; Akers deploys the
KU-band communications antenna

<p>
<dt>06:54 a.m.
<dd>Akers deploys the PLB radiators to help cool Atlantis' avionics systems

<p>
<dt>07:34 a.m.
<dd>Readdy and Wilcutt conduct an initial rendezvous burn to refine Atlantis'
path to the Mir; Walz activates the Commercial Protein Crystal Growth
experiment

<p>
<dt>07:54 a.m.
<dd>Private medical conference

<p>
<dt>08:54 a.m.
<dd>Atlantis crew sleep begins

<p>
<dt>01:54 p.m.
<dd>Mir 22 crew sleep begins (9 hours)
</dl>



