<HEAD>
	<TITLE>SPACEZONE &#149; SPACE NEWS</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<!--Copyrigh© 1996 Warner International Communications Group, Inc. All Rights Reserved.-->
<P><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#1113AB" VLINK="#B40FB"
ALINK="#F0051" >
<BODY>

<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="395" HEIGHT="119" SRC="art/szlogo.gif" ALT="SpaceZone">
<BR CLEAR="all">
<IMG ALIGN="left" WIDTH="198" HEIGHT="198" SRC="art/patch.gif"ALT="STS-79 Patch">
<BR>
<P>
<H1>Astronaut Exchange
<BR>Shuttle Mission STS-79</H1>
<BR>

 <H2><A HREF="time.htm">Mission Timeline</A></H2>
 <H2>Flight Day 7</H2>
 
 <BR CLEAR="all">
 
<p>September 21, 1996</p>
<dl>

<p>
<dt>08:54 p.m.
<dd>Atlantis and Mir 22 crew wakeup

<p>
<dt>11:54 p.m.
<dd>The astronauts and cosmonauts conduct a daily tagup on transfer and
flight plan activities
</dl>
<p>September 22, 1996
<dl>
<p>
<dt>12:24 a.m.
<dd>Transfer activities resume as Lucid and Blaha continue their handover

<p>
<dt>12:54 a.m.
<dd>CREW CHOICE TV WITH WALZ

<p>
<dt>01:19 a.m.
<dd>Apt exercises

<p>
<dt>02:54 a.m.
<dd>Walz uses the IMAX camera to shoot scenes of Apt and Akers working in
the Priroda module; Lucid exercises on the Mir treadmill; Korzun exercises on
the Mir ergometer

<p>
<dt>03:54 a.m.
<dd>Walz helps Blaha and Korzun transfer the MIDAS experiment from the
Spacehab to Priroda which will be use to study superconductor materials in
weightlessness

<p>
<dt>05:54 a.m.
<dd>Akers sets up the IMAX camera in the Mir Core Module

<p>
<dt>05:59 a.m.
<dd>U.S. PAO Opportunity with Readdy, Wilcutt, Lucid, Blaha and Korzun on
either the Shuttle Flight Deck or in the Spacehab module

<p>
<dt>06:24 a.m.
<dd>Walz continues the photographic survey of the Mir through the Spacehab
overhead windows; Lucid and Blaha exchange dosimeters to measure
radiation levels in the Mir; Korzun completes the setup of the IMAX camera in
the Mir Core Module

<p>
<dt>06:54 a.m.
<dd>Akers exercises

<p>
<dt>07:24 a.m.
<dd>Transfer activities continue for all crewmembers

<p>
<dt>07:39 a.m.
<dd>Walz exercises

<p>
<dt>08:09 a.m.
<dd>Wilcutt exercises

<p>
<dt>08:39 a.m.
<dd>Lucid exercises on the Mir treadmill

<p>
<dt>09:24 a.m.
<dd>The astronauts and cosmonauts conduct a daily tagup on transfer and
flight plan activities

<p>
<dt>10:49 a.m.
<dd>Private medical conference

<p>
<dt>11:04 a.m.
<dd>Akers conducts a private family conference

<p>
<dt>12:54 p.m.
<dd>Atlantis and Mir 22 crew sleep begins</dl>


