<P>
<H1>Astronaut Exchange
<BR>Shuttle Mission STS-79</H1>
<BR>

 <H2><A HREF="time.htm">Mission Timeline</A></H2>
 <H2>Flight Day 11</H2>
 
 <BR CLEAR="all">
 
<p>September 25, 1996
<dl>

<p>
<dt>09:54 p.m.
<dd>Atlantis crew wakeup

<p>
<dt>10:54 p.m.
<dd>Private medical conference

<p>
<dt>12:09 a.m.
<dd>Walz stows the Orbiter Docking System for entry and landing
</dl>
<p>September 26, 1996
<dl>
<p>
<dt>12:54 a.m.
<dd>Walz and Lucid prepare biomedical sensors for Lucid for entry, landing
and postlanding data collection

<p>
<dt>01:09 a.m.
<dd>Apt and Walz deactivate Spacehab systems and close out the module

<p>
<dt>02:09 a.m.
<dd>The astronauts begin deorbit preparations

<p>
<dt>03:28 a.m.
<dd>PLBD closing

<p>
<dt>06:08 a.m.
<dd>Deorbit burn

<p>
<dt>07:12 a.m.
<dd>ATLANTIS LANDS AT THE KENNEDY SPACE CENTER</dl>



