<H2>HOW TO ORDER</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<B>
1. Select the volume(s) or set(s) you would like to order.
<P>
2. Fill out the Shipping and Billing information below.
<P>
3. Fax the order form to 1-972-255-5655.</B>
<P>
<FONT SIZE="-1">
Indicate the volume(s) you would like to order by placing an [X] in the space next to the volume number/video tilte.
<P>
Member Price $6.99 ea. - Non-Member Price $8.99 ea. 
Shipping & Handling $4.00 (1 to 3 volumes) Add $1.00 for each additional volume
<P>
