<h3 align=center><font size=3>South Florida Regional Planning Council</font></h3>
<p align=center><font size=4>Council Members</font></p>
<p align=center>&#160;</p>
<hr>
<p align=center>A leader in the South Florida region of Broward, Dade, and Monroe Counties, the Council is composed of 19 voting 
members including county and municipal elected officials and Governor's appointees. The Council has a five-member 
Executive Committee consisting of council officers and the immediate past chairman. The Executive Committee, in 
conjunction with the remaining 14 members, constitute the full Council. Four additional ex-officio members representing the 
South Florida Water Management District and the Florida Departments of Transportation, Commerce, and Environmental 
Protection sit on the Council.</p>
<p><b>EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE</b> </p>
<p>Jimmy Weekley, Chair</p>
<p>Natacha Millan, Vice-Chair</p>
<p>Richard Krinzman, Treasurer</p>
<p>Emmett McTigue, Secretary</p>
<p>Scott Cowan, Immediate Past Chair</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
