<html>

<head>
<title>South Florida Regional Planning Council</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1">
<meta name="South Florida Regional Planning Council" content="">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body background="images/wlogoppr.jpg">
<p><!--Broward Dade Monroe coordination redevelopment intergovernmental--><!--Hollywood economic environment demographics coastal hurricane--><!--Miami Fort Lauderdale transportation facilitation public policy--><!--hazardous materials alternative fuels land use Everglades Keys--><!--Biscayne strategic affordable housing visioning Clean Cities--><!--growth dispute resolution regional Florida planning--></p>
<p align=center><img src="images/sfrpcgp.gif" align=bottom width=288 height=144> </p>
<h1 align=center>South Florida Regional Planning Council</h1>
<p align=center>The South Florida Regional Planning Council is a planning and public policy agency which works with public and private leadership in the South Florida Region 
to achieve a vision of the future.</p>
<hr>
<h3><a href="council/menu1.htm"><img src="images/counsm.gif" alt="*" align=top border=0 width=53 height=54><font size=3>The Council</font></a> </h3>
<dl>
<dd>Information about the SFRPC, its mission and services, its members and staff, a comprehensive regional directory, and a visitor response form.<br>
</dd>
</dl>
<h3><a href="whatsnew/menu2.htm"><img src="images/whnewsm.gif" alt="*" align=top border=0 width=35 height=54><font size=3>What's New in South Florida</font></a> </h3>
<dl>
<dd>Activities in and around the region, including highlights of Council activities, meeting agendas and a schedule of upcoming events. </dd>
<dd><a href="whatsnew/whatnew1.htm"><img src="images/diambut.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=14 height=15> Eastward Ho! Local Government Resource Center</a> </dd>
<dd><a href="whatsnew/whatnew2.htm"><img src="images/diambut.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=14 height=15> Broward County's Human Service Delivery System Model Workshop</a> </dd>
<dd><a href="whatsnew/whatnew3.htm"><img src="images/diambut.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=14 height=15> Visioning for Lower Matecumbe Key</a> </dd>
<dd>&nbsp;</dd>
</dl>
<h3><a href="websites/menu3.htm"><img src="images/websitsm.gif" alt="*" align=top border=0 width=53 height=54><font size=3>Related Web Sites</font></a> </h3>
<dl>
<dd>Our collection of Hotlinks to South Florida, state and federal agencies and other points of interest in the region. <br>
</dd>
</dl>
<h3><a href="region/menu4.htm"><img src="images/regionsm.gif" alt="*" align=top border=0 width=47 height=54><font size=3>Our Region</font></a> </h3>
<dl>
<dd>Profiles of the demographics, economics and environmental issues of South Florida and its counties and cities, including graphs, tables and maps. <br>
</dd>
</dl>
<h3><a href="current/menu5.htm"><img src="images/currntsm.gif" alt="*" align=top border=0 width=50 height=54><font size=3>Current Issues in South Florida</font></a> </h3>
<dl>
<dd>Information about current SFRPC programs and projects at the SFRPC, including the <i>Strategic Regional Policy Plan for South Florida,</i> local plan 
review, developments of regional impact, the Local Emergency Planning Committee, Clean Cities, Eastward Ho! and more! <br>
<br>
</dd>
<div align=center><center>
<dt>There have been <img src=http://www.target.net/webtools/counter/8.gif>
<img src=http://www.target.net/webtools/counter/0.gif>
<img src=http://www.target.net/webtools/counter/1.gif>
Visitors to this site since 11/22/96. </dt>
</center></div>
<dd>&nbsp;</dd>
</dl>
