<p align=center>South Florida Regional Planning Council</p>
<h3 align=center>Related Web Sites</h3>
<h3 align=center>South Florida Municipalities </h3>
<p>South Florida has a total of 61 municipalities in Broward, Dade and Monroe Counties. The cities, towns and villages are 
listed below in alphabetical order. Active names will take you to official municipal web sites. If you would like a summary 
directory of names, addresses and telephone numbers, go to the <a href="../council/menu15.htm">Regional Directory</a>. If you would like to see brief profile, 
go to Municipal Profiles.</p>
