<body background="../images/plogoppr.jpg">
<p align=center>South Florida Regional Planning Council</p>
<p align=center><font size=4><b>Council Programs</b> </font></p>
<p align=center><font size=4><b>Florida Gold Coast Clean Cities Coalition</b></font></p>
<p align=center><img src="../images/cleancit.gif" alt="cleancit.gif" align=bottom width=72 height=54> </p>
