<DOCHDR>
http://www.sfrpc.com:80/current/fmrissum.htm 199.227.154.96 19970110050405 text/html 6672
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 05:09:48 GMT
Server: Stronghold/1.3.2 Ben-SSL/1.3 Apache/1.1.1
