<DOCOLDNO>IA090-000961-B027-72</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sfrpc.com:80/current/srppgoal.htm 199.227.154.96 19970110050504 text/html 8752
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 05:10:44 GMT
Server: Stronghold/1.3.2 Ben-SSL/1.3 Apache/1.1.1
