<DOCHDR>
http://www.sfrpc.com:80/current/cccover.htm 199.227.154.96 19970110052357 text/html 7108
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 05:29:41 GMT
Server: Stronghold/1.3.2 Ben-SSL/1.3 Apache/1.1.1
