<TITLE>Organisation of NERC</TITLE>
</HEAD> 
<BODY><H1><IMG SRC="/images/nerclarg.gif"></H1>
<HR>
<H2>Organisation of NERC</H2>

<P>
There are NERC research laboratories throughout the UK, which are grouped 
administratively into five main Centres and Surveys.  
</p><p>
The central administrative office for NERC is based in Swindon, sharing a 
building with four of the other Research Councils.
</p><P>
The specialist and technical services required by university researchers and 
NERC's own staff are looked after by NERC Scientific Services.  
</p><p>
Some specific research areas are covered in specialists units, largely 
funded by NERC but based within universities.
</p><p>
Special programmes and initiatives are set up as required, frequently in 
collaboration with other organisations.     

</P><P></P>
