<TITLE>JANET Acceptable Use Policy</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1><B>JANET Acceptable Use Policy</B></H1>
<HR>
<P>
The JISC (Joint Information Systems Committee) has recently undertaken a review of the <A HREF="http://www.ja.net/newsfiles/documents/documents/use.doc">Acceptable Use
Policy</A> for those organisations, including NERC, authorised to use
JANET. This comes into immediate effect, replacing the previous Acceptable
Use Guidelines document.
</P><P>
The Policy document gives details of the acceptable and unacceptable uses
of the JANET network and must be adhered to by all NERC staff.
</P>
<P></P><P>
</P>
<HR>
