<H1 align=center>
Who's Who
</H1>
<h2 align=center>
A list of NCS staff and their locations
</h2>
<hr>
<p>
E-mail Ids: The usernames shown below are Novell GroupWise (WordPerfect Office)
usernames and are obtainable from the Address Book.
<p>
The Internet address format for NERC GroupWise users is:
<p>
<pre>
       id@wpo.nerc.ac.uk
e.g.  hjd@wpo.nerc.ac.uk
</pre>
or just hjd if mailing from within Novell GroupWise.
<p>
Also NCS staff can be mailed as:
<br>
<pre>
       Initial.Surname@computer-services.nerc.ac.uk
or
       Initial.Surname@ncs.nerc.ac.uk
e.g.   J.Down@ncs.nerc.ac.uk
</pre>
<p>
See 
<A HREF="/ncs/mail/staffmai.html">
Mailing NERC Staff
</A>
for further details.
</p>
