Monk's Wood<br>
Abbots Ripton<br>
Huntingdon PE17 2LS<br>
<P>
Tel +44 1487 773381<br>
Tlx 32416 MONITE G<br>
Fax +44 1487 773467<br>
<P>
r.parsell@ncs.nerc.ac.uk
<P>
