<HEAD>
<!-- SS~~0001 -->
<Title>Teaching FIRST</title>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<BODY BACKGROUND="teach2.jpg" >

<H1>A SOCIETY EXISTS ONLY AS LONG AS ITS CHILDREN LEARN</H1>

<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=5>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>
<TD>
<H2>How do we teach???</H2>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="gradeorg.htm">What does our K-6 curriculum look like?</A> <P>
<LI><A HREF="samples.htm">Samples of our hands-on science</A><P>

<LI><A HREF="makediff.htm">Only Actual Results count</A><P>
