</UL>
<ALIGN=LEFT>Our prices are deliberately low so that everyone can learn, OR teach!
<P>

<HR>
<P>
<DT><A HREF="goodtchg.htm">Good Teaching Conquers Problems</A>
<DD>The "How To" guide to Good Teaching Practices. More than a week of inservice materials and ideas written by award-winning mentor teachers who want all children to benefit from quality teaching.<P>

<P>


<HR>
<P>
<H2>THINGS ARE CHANGING</H2>
<DT><A HREF="directn.htm">Where Is Science Education Going?</A>
<DD>Science Education has entered a new age. It is now recognized that telling the students what has been discovered in the past is not enough.
<P><P>


<P>
