<Title>Coming Soon</title>

</HEAD>


<BODY BGCOLOR=#99AAFF>
<center>
<H1>COMING SOON....</H1>
<HR>
Our next attraction: <B>The Interactive Space Science Involvement Program.</B><BR>
<I>(Based on the NASA/NSTA contest of the same name.)</I><P>
</CENTER>

We will be visiting the EXPLORING SCIENCE Academy to work with a SciTeam&#153 made up of four SciKids&#153. They will walk you through the new study of <B>"Visioneering" &#153 </B><P>

<B>"Visioneering" &#153 </B> is the science of solving more than one problem with a single solution. The SciKids&#153 create a solution for the immediate problem, then they seek other problems that they can solve with their solution. Sometimes they have to solve other problems to create a solution for their original problem. In any case, solutions to problems become affordable when the cost can spread over more than one problem.<P>

<HR>
In the first two episodes, they will demonstrate the problem solving skills and techniques that led to the real team's successful entry in the NASA/NSTA contest. After that we will present the problem and you the students will be allowed to put in your suggestions. The following week, the students around the country will vote on the best suggestions. In this way, an interactive problem solving solution will evolve from students around the country. After the solution is reached, the actual solution submitted by real students will be presented.<P>

The goal is to have fun solving the world's problems. The winning teams certainly did!
<HR>
<center>
<H2>The SciTeam&#153</H2>
</center>

<table border=5>
<tr>
<td>
<IMG SRC="scieric2.jpg" ><P>
</td>

<td>
Hi, I'm Eric. In any sport, I score. When I'm not on the field, I make sure that the SciTeam is not pursuing the impossible. Like Charles Drew, I want to help humanity!<P>
<B>"The Doer"</B><P>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<IMG SRC="scitess3.jpg" ><P>
</td>

<td>
Hi, I'm Tessie. I have great ideas. No problem exists that I do not think of a way to solve it! The two hats are for my favorite baseball teams and the three watches are for my favorite time zones.<P>
<B>"The Thinker"</B><P>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<IMG SRC="scimary2.jpg" ><P>
</td>

<td>
Hi, I'm Mary. I want to know "Why?" Why does it work? Why doesn't it work? Until all of the answers are in and written down, the problem is not solved.<P>
<B>"The Questioner"</B><P>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>
<IMG SRC="scitony2.jpg" ><P>
</td>

<td>
Hi, I'm Tony. The others on the team have great ideas, but none of them seem to work properly until I get my hands on them. I find a way to make them work.<P>
<B>"The Maker"</B><P>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<P>
