The four SciTeam(tm) members are on the beach.<BR>
<I>"Ouch,"</I> says Tessie.<BR>
<I>"Oooh,"</I> says Tony.<BR>
<I>"It hurts,"</I> says Mary.<BR>
<I>"AaaG, to the shade!"</I> exclaims Eric.<P>

Eric leads the race to the shade of nearby trees.<P>

<I>"I know why I have a sunburn,"</I> says Tessie. <I>"But, why do you have one Eric?"</I><BR>
<I>"I heard somewhere that sunburns were going to become a bigger problem in the future because there is a hole in the atmosphere,"</I> says Mary.<BR>
<I>"If there is a hole, we got to plug it right away. Sunburns cause pain!"</I> says Eric.<BR>
<I>"The library and Internet will help us get us started!,"</I> says Tony.<P>

