<Title>EXPLORING SCIENCE</Title>
<H1>A Curriculum for the 21st Century</H1>

The goal of this program is to produce a nation of science literates - NO MATTER WHAT FIELD THEY ATTEMPT. The grade levels spiral, with each grade level more sophisticated than the previous. Each chapter does thematic hands-on science. Each lesson emphasizes scientific processes and problem solving. The total program is based on a full integrated curriculum, as is required to accomplish the goals of any elementary curriculum.<P>
<B><I>The graduate of this program will have a strong foundation in science and be ready for the future.</I></B><P><P>

<H2>BOOK K (grade appropriate K -1 text, K-1 research )</H2>
(A 95% total Kindergarten curriculum, including manipulatives, wrapped in an exciting science framework.)<P>

