 <I>Messages to Our Brain</I> - <P>

<I>Our Tongue Sends</I>_____________Sweet, sour, bitter, and salty;_______comparing, categorizing, predicting, inferring.<BR>
 <I>Messages to Our Brain</I> -<P> 

