<DOCNO>WT08-B35-269</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA053-000899-B015-225</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.macropress.com:80/numbers.htm 205.230.198.231 19970111232606 text/html 8169
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 23:25:01 GMT
