Diamond Bar High School<BR>
21400 E. Pathfinder Road<BR>
Diamond Bar, CA  91765<P><P>

Author/Teacher/Advisor: Leigh Hoven Severson<BR>
Chief Editor of the K-6 EXPLORING SCIENCE curriculum that is written to the NEW 1995 US Science Standards.
